metadata.name: NFSC - Greatest Mints
metadata.description:
Spend a lifetime digging through crates looking for that perfect diamond in the rough. That first record you put on in the morning to pump you up before your day. That last song you put on as you dim the lights and wind down your evening. Look no further, Non Fungible Social Club has it all. Summer bangers, hypnotic slow jams, deep cuts, and timeless classics.

For Fans Of: Art, Big Brains  
Rating: 5 out of 5
